@baseUrl = http://localhost:4004

### Health CAP
GET {{baseUrl}}/

### Sync repository (mock ou real)
POST {{baseUrl}}/grounding/syncRepository
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "repositoryId": "mock-repo",
  "folderPath": "/",
  "limit": 20
}

### List documents
GET {{baseUrl}}/grounding/SourceDocuments

### Generate chunks (substitua o UUID)
POST {{baseUrl}}/grounding/generateChunks
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "documentID": "00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000",
  "chunkSize": 900,
  "overlap": 150
}

### List chunks
GET {{baseUrl}}/grounding/DocumentChunks

### Semantic search
POST {{baseUrl}}/grounding/semanticSearch
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "query": "como configurar destination no dms",
  "topK": 5
}
